title: Did ‘The Simpsons’ Predict Pro-Trump Horned Rioter Jake Angeli?
subtitle: Either way, we love the character name "Groundskeeper Willie."
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The character Goundskeeper Willie was once depicted in an episode of "The Simpsons" in similar horned attire worn by one of the pro-Trump rioters in D.C. on Jan. 6, 2021.
